Nakuru County Deputy Director of Political Affairs, Snr Sgt (Rtd) Wilfred Chebochok, has succumbed to Covid-19 while undergoing treatment at the Nakuru Nursing Home. 

A source at the hospital said the county official was admitted to the intensive care unit (ICU) last week after developing breathing complications. 



